Figured out it was because of js conflict - ckeditor and mptt-admin js. So, here is the work around. In jquery_namespace.js file, make it look like below. Just added ```$.noConflict();``` 
```
$.noConflict();
window.$ = django.jQuery;
window.jQuery = django.jQuery;
```
Further information http://api.jquery.com/jQuery.noConflict/

